@startuml
title DAI — Sequence Diagram (Post-opératoire / SSPI)

actor "Equipe SSPI" as SSPI
participant "DAI Frontend (SSPI)" as FE
participant "DAI Backend API" as BE
participant "PostOp Module" as POSTOP
database "DAI Database" as DB

== Démarrage séjour SSPI ==
SSPI -> FE : Ouvrir écran postop
FE -> BE : StartPostOpStay(caseId)
BE -> POSTOP : startStay(caseId)
POSTOP -> DB : Create PostOpStay
DB --> POSTOP : Stay active
POSTOP --> BE : Stay started
BE --> FE : StayReady

== Observation postop ==
SSPI -> FE : Saisir observation postop
FE -> BE : POST observation
BE -> POSTOP : saveObservation
POSTOP -> DB : Save PostOpObservation
DB --> POSTOP : Observation saved

== Calcul Aldrete ==
POSTOP -> POSTOP : compute Aldrete
POSTOP -> DB : Save ClinicalScore(ALDRETE)
DB --> POSTOP : Score saved
POSTOP --> BE : Observation + score + readiness
BE --> FE : Afficher score Aldrete

== Consultation ==
SSPI -> FE : Consulter score de sortie
FE -> BE : GET /scores/aldrete
BE -> POSTOP : getAldrete(caseId)
POSTOP -> DB : Load latest observation + score
DB --> POSTOP : Data
POSTOP --> BE : Aldrete payload
BE --> FE : Afficher score

== Fin séjour ==
SSPI -> FE : Terminer séjour SSPI
FE -> BE : EndPostOpStay(caseId)
BE -> POSTOP : endStay(caseId)
POSTOP -> DB : Update stay ended
DB --> POSTOP : OK
POSTOP --> BE : Stay ended
BE --> FE : Confirmation
@enduml